CAST:
 Visit this link: http://wwwimage.cbs.com/cms/files/images/primetime/harpers_island/cast/cast_thumb120_abby_mills.jpg
Abby Mills (Elaine Cassidy) is a natural beauty in her mid-20s who hails from Harper's Island. She is the groom's best friend and his wedding brings her back to the island for the first time since her mother was murdered seven years ago. Abby's father, the local Sheriff, gunned down the psychopath at the end of his killing spree, but the event shattered Abby's relationship with her dad and left her haunted by her mother's death and the memory of the man who killed her.


 Visit this link: http://wwwimage.cbs.com/cms/files/images/primetime/harpers_island/cast/cast_thumb120_beth_barrington.jpg
Beth Barrington (Amber Borycki) is a bridesmaid and Trish's former college roommate. She's beautiful, energetic and athletic. Though she didn't grow up as privileged as Trish, she's very comfortable in that world.


 Visit this link: http://wwwimage.cbs.com/cms/files/images/primetime/harpers_island/cast/cast_thumb120_cal_vandeusen.jpg
Cal Vandeusen (Adam Campbell) is Chloe's boyfriend and a doctor. He's a charming British outsider who doesn't know anyone in the wedding party, but tries to fit in with the tight knit group. He treats Chloe like gold, and bought an engagement ring before ever stepping foot on Harper's Island. As he waits for the right moment to pop the question, things keep getting in the way and at times the frustration causes his "nice guy" demeanor to fall away and reveal something darker.

 Visit this link: http://wwwimage.cbs.com/cms/files/images/primetime/harpers_island/cast/cast_thumb120_chloe_carter.jpg
Chloe Carter (Cameron Richardson) is one of Trish's bridesmaids. She's sexy, playful, impulsive and always looking for ways to live life to the fullest. She has a surprising curiosity about serial killers, especially John Wakefield. But beneath the blonde bombshell exterior is an intelligent woman searching for romance and love.

 Visit this link: http://wwwimage.cbs.com/cms/files/images/primetime/harpers_island/cast/cast_thumb120_christoper_sullivan.jpg
Christopher 'Sully' Sullivan (Matt Barr) is Henry's best man. All of his friends call him Sully, and he has lots of friends. He's a fun-loving frat boy at heart whose good buddies live vicariously through his many sexual escapades. He's been Henry's best friend since high school, but it's questionable if he's at the wedding more for Henry's benefit or for the bachelor party and bridesmaids, particularly when he gets and eyeful of Chloe.
